blog.name: tsingadark
blog.title: Let's go, baby
blog.description: Skye. 24. Fanfic writer. AO3 & Twitter. Jikook Big Bang Weekly Fic Rec Multifandom blog. Mostly BTS at this point. They've taken over my life. (Yoonkook and Jikook make me cry)

title: Weekly Fic Rec
body:
the list this week is really short since orientation week started and I’ve been super busy. too busy to read as many fanfics as I usually read lol

Yoonkook

i know places by notyoongs
T | 5.1k | canon compliant, magical realism | Jungkook is a shapeshifter who can shift into a bunny, except he can’t control when and where, so Yoongi has to take care of him when he does. this is honestly such a cute fic. bunny!jungkook will always be one of my fav things

Delivered by RNA
M | 17.1k | AU | Texting fic in which Jungkook is given the wrong number and ends up texting Yoongi instead of the girl who gave him the number. This fic was so sweet and funny, I wish I could read it again for the first time.

of first kisses and bitter coffee by taers
T | 3.4k | canon compliant | fic about Jungkook getting his first kiss from Yoongi. this was my second time reading this fic but I just had to include it here because I enjoyed it just as much the second time around!!

Jinkook

light at the end by fruitily
T | 6.7k | AU | fic with grim reaper seokjin and college student jungkook with a happy ending. honestly, such a sweet fic! 11/10 would recommend

2Seok

Take a Chip and Dip Me Low by @theembarrassedpotato
T | 4k | AU | the title is already funny and I promise you will love this fic. It’s about Seokjin thinking he signed up for a salsa (the dip) class when really it’s a salsa (the dance) class :D
